reviewText: Not good at all. The photography is not professional. Not clear. The girls are not that pretty. The outfits are bad. The one saving grace would be Barbi but her outfit was street walker type not high class call girl. I wish John Cross would ask us about the shoes these girls usually wear. Backless, extreme high heels are ugly. That's my opinion anyway. I'd skip this DVD.
This show is fine but not great.  The cover girl is the best but most of the woman here are not very good looking.
